<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[اللَّهَق]</span>،<span class="c5"> بالقاف:</span> الأبيض،<span class="c5"> والأنثى:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
