<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و <span class="c4">[اللَّهى]</span>: جمع: لهاة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعْلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
